title: Tropisch Nederland, Part 1 [Tropical Dutch East Indies] in color! (1939)

sources.title: De Oldify Tropisch Nederland Deel 1 Audio 1080p S Ai
sources.description: This is part-1 of a 8 part documentary about the Dutch East Indies (currently Indonesia) just before WW-II. This footage has been meticulously restored, enhanced and colorized with the lastest A.I. video software.
